'''正義路（Jhengyi Rd.）'''為[[高雄市|高雄市]][[三民區|三民區]]及[[苓雅區|苓雅區]]的南北向道路<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/local/paper/275592 |title=排除鐵路地下化 正義路居民怨 |access-date=2020-07-10 |archive-date=2020-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200710063637/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/local/paper/275592 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，北起於[[九如一路|九如一路]]口，南止於正義路10巷口銜接正義路3巷，是往來[[三民區|三民區]]、[[苓雅區|苓雅區]]的重要道路。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://house.ettoday.net/news/1735550 |title=台鐵捷運化　高雄軌道宅首購區1字頭可入手 |access-date=2020-07-10 |archive-date=2020-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102093714/https://house.ettoday.net/news/1735550 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

